    <item>
      <title>卡尼、弗里兰领衔继任特鲁多出任加拿大总理的候选人名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/carney-freeland-lead-list-of-contenders-to-succeed-trudeau-as-canada-s-pm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贾斯汀·特鲁多周一表示，他将在未来几个月卸任加拿大总理一职，结束他连续三次赢得选举和九年担任加拿大最高政治职务的政治生涯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/carney-freeland-lead-list-of-contenders-to-succeed-trudeau-as-canada-s-pm</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 19:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>骚乱四年后特朗普在选举仪式上被宣布为获胜者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trump-declared-election-winner-in-ceremony-four-years-after-riot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国会周一毫无争议地批准了唐纳德·特朗普的总统大选胜利，并由他击败的民主党对手卡马拉·哈里斯主持选举，恢复了四年前美国国会大厦遭暴徒袭击、选举计票失败后的民主仪式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trump-declared-election-winner-in-ceremony-four-years-after-riot</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 18:55:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅洛尼与马斯克和特朗普的亲密关系是双赢的，但也有巨大的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/meloni-s-closeness-to-musk-and-trump-is-a-win-win-and-a-big-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔治亚·梅洛尼在海湖庄园待了不到五个小时，每一刻都至关重要。有这么多领导人在争夺唐纳德·特朗普的注意力，她赢了。但在与当选总统共进晚餐后，她坐下来观看了一部关于约翰·伊斯特曼的有争议的纪录片，约翰·伊斯特曼是特朗普的盟友，他制定了一项推翻 2020 年大选结果的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/meloni-s-closeness-to-musk-and-trump-is-a-win-win-and-a-big-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 18:12:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙警告伊朗核计划已接近无可挽回的地步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/macron-warns-iran-s-nuclear-program-close-to-point-of-no-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙警告称，伊朗核计划可能正走向不可逆转的道路，已接近无法挽回的地步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/macron-warns-iran-s-nuclear-program-close-to-point-of-no-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 17:57:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多执政九年后辞职，自由党迫使他下台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trudeau-resigns-after-nine-years-in-power-as-liberals-force-him-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于支持率下滑和党内反叛，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多在领导加拿大九年多后宣布辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trudeau-resigns-after-nine-years-in-power-as-liberals-force-him-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 16:10:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克为何涉足英国儿童性侵团伙丑闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/why-is-elon-musk-criticizing-keir-starmer-over-uk-grooming-gang-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克指责英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 参与了数十年前发生的儿童性剥削团伙丑闻，此举让英国政府陷入守势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/why-is-elon-musk-criticizing-keir-starmer-over-uk-grooming-gang-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 15:11:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普寻求推迟对封口费的判决以提起上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trump-asks-new-york-appeals-court-to-stop-hush-money-sentencing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普请求纽约一名法官推迟原定于 1 月 10 日作出的封口费判决，以便这位当选总统可以在就职典礼前对此案的有罪判决提出质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trump-asks-new-york-appeals-court-to-stop-hush-money-sentencing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 14:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管房地产丑闻不断，斯塔默仍支持市部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/starmer-backs-city-minister-tulip-siddiq-amid-property-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 表示，他仍然对金融城部长图利普·西迪克 (Tulip Siddiq) 充满信心，后者因与孟加拉国被罢免的前政府盟友的房产有联系而受到审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/starmer-backs-city-minister-tulip-siddiq-amid-property-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 12:48:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿萨德倒台后美国允许向叙利亚提供更多人道主义援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/us-set-to-allow-for-more-humanitarian-aid-to-flow-to-syria</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在叙利亚总统巴沙尔·阿萨德倒台后，拜登政府向叙利亚提供有限的制裁解除，以增加人道主义援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/us-set-to-allow-for-more-humanitarian-aid-to-flow-to-syria</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 03:46:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉挑战者会见拜登，向特朗普施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/venezuela-challenger-to-meet-biden-putting-pressure-on-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普入主华盛顿的几天前，这位被美国承认为当选总统的委内瑞拉反对派领导人与总统乔·拜登会面，并面临着如何处理与这个无证移民主要来源国的关系的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/venezuela-challenger-to-meet-biden-putting-pressure-on-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 02:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
